snippet.title: Math Blaster Jr. (1996)
snippet.description: Hey kids, grab your pencils and paper and join the Blaster Pals on an intergalactic math adventure. Play along with GC, Blasternaut, and Spot as their adventure takes them to four fun filled mathematical planets. Parents, help your child solve the math problems the Blaster Pals come across.
